<%# app/views/predictions/rules.html.erb %>

<%= render 'layouts/shared/page_header',
    title: "Stigagjöf og reglur",
    breadcrumbs: [{ name: t('common.home'), path: root_path }, { name: "Reglur" }] %>

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 pb-32">

  <%# 1. TIME DEADLINE CARD %>
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm mb-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#f9faf9] rounded-bl-full -z-10 opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
      <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"></div>
      <h2 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Skilafrestur spáa</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[14px] text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      Lokað er fyrir allar spár nákvæmlega <strong class="text-[#0a1d13]">10 mínútum áður en leikur hefst</strong> (samkvæmt opinberum upphafstíma leiksins).
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-3 border border-slate-100">
      <span class="text-[11px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-600 bg-red-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md shrink-0">
        Dæmi
      </span>
      <p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 font-mono">
        Ef leikur hefst klukkan 19:00, læsist leikurinn í kerfinu sjálfkrafa klukkan 18:50. Eftir það er ómögulegt að breyta eða vista spá.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 2. CORE CONCEPT CARD %>
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] mb-3">Hvernig virkar kerfið?</h2>
    <p class="text-[14px] text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      Stigagjöfin reiknast sjálfkrafa út frá þremur nákvæmum flokkum eftir að leik lýkur. Kerfið verðlaunar ríkulega fyrir hárrétt úrslit,
      en dregur úr stigum eftir því sem spáin fjarlægist lokastöðuna.
    </p>
  </div>

  <%# 3. POINTS DISTRIBUTION CARD %>
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] mb-4">Stigaliðir</h2>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <%# Tier 1 %>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-slate-50">
        <div class="h-8 min-w-[32px] px-2 rounded-xl bg-[#0a1d13] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shrink-0 shadow-sm">
          25
        </div>
        <div class="min-w-0">
          <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] leading-tight">Hárrétt niðurstaða</div>
          <div class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">Bæði heimalið og útilið með nákvæmlega rétta markatölu.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Tier 2 %>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-slate-50">
        <div class="h-8 min-w-[32px] px-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[#2d5a43] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shrink-0 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
          10-20
        </div>
        <div class="min-w-0">
          <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] leading-tight">Rétt úrslit (Heimasigur / Jafntefli / Útisigur)</div>
          <div class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">
            Þú spáir réttum sigurvegara eða jafntefli byggt á hlutfalli mismunarins (<span class="font-mono bg-slate-50 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-slate-600">sign</span>). Þú byrjar með 20 stig en færð frádrátt fyrir skekkju í mörkum og markamismun. Þú færð þó <strong>aldrei minna en 10 stig</strong> ef táknið er rétt.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Tier 3 %>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="h-8 min-w-[32px] px-2 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 font-bold font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shrink-0 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
          0-4
        </div>
        <div class="min-w-0">
          <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] leading-tight">Nálægðarstig (Hræætan)</div>
          <div class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">
            Ef þú klúðrar úrslitunum (spáir t.d. heimasigri en leikurinn endar með jafntefli) geturðu samt krækt í allt að 4 sárabótastig ef mörkin sem þú spáðir voru nálægt lokastöðunni.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 4. SCENARIO A: DECISIVE WIN %>
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] mb-1">Dæmi A: Leikur endar með sigri (2 - 1)</h2>
    <p class="text-[12px] font-mono text-slate-400 mb-6">Ef lokastaða leiksins er 2 - 1:</p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <%# Example 1: Exact Sync %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 2 - 1</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#0a1d13] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+25 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Hárrétt úrslit gefa fullan bónus.</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 2: Correct Outcome, Imperfect GD %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 3 - 1</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#2d5a43] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+17 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rétt tákn (heimasigur). Skekkjan er 1 mark á heimaliðinu og 1 mark á markamismuninum (20 - (1 × 2) - 1 = 17).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 3: Correct Outcome, Perfect GD %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 1 - 0</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#2d5a43] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+16 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rétt tákn (heimasigur). Mismunurinn er réttur (+1), en vantar 2 mörk upp á heildarsamsvörun (20 - (2 × 2) - 0 = 16).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 4: Correct Outcome, Perfect Goal Difference Margin %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 4 - 3</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#2d5a43] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+12 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rétt úrslit (heimasigur) og fullkominn markamismunur (+1). Þótt mörkin séu mörg, þá bjargar rétti mismunurinn spánni (20 - (4 × 2) - 0 = 12).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 5: Correct Outcome, High Error Margin %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 4 - 0</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#2d5a43] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+11 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rétt tákn (heimasigur). Mikil markaskekkja dregur úr stigum en hrynur ekki niður úr gólfinu (20 - (3 × 2) - 3 = 11).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 6: Incorrect Outcome, High Scavenger %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 1 - 1</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-slate-600 bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+3 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rangt tákn (jafntefli), en Hræætan gefur 3 stig þar sem heildarmarkaskekkjan var aðeins 1 mark á heimaliðinu (4 - 1 = 3).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 7: Incorrect Outcome, Precise Goal Volume (The Scavenger) %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 1 - 2</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-slate-600 bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+2 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rangt tákn (útisigur í stað heimasigurs), en Hræætan gefur þér samt 2 stig vegna þess að heildarmarkaskekkjan þín var aðeins 2 mörk samtals (4 - 2 = 2).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 5. SCENARIO B: SCORE DRAW %>
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13] mb-1">Dæmi B: Leikur endar með jafntefli (1 - 1)</h2>
    <p class="text-[12px] font-mono text-slate-400 mb-6">Ef lokastaða leiksins er 1 - 1:</p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <%# Example 1: Exact Draw Sync %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 1 - 1</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#0a1d13] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+25 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Hárrétt jafntefli gefur fullan bónus.</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 2: Symmetrical Draw Error %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 2 - 2</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white bg-[#2d5a43] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+16 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rétt tákn (jafntefli). Mismunurinn passar (0), en mörkin eru tveimur of mörg (20 - (2 × 2) - 0 = 16).</p>
      </div>

      <%# Example 3: Wrong Outcome Scavenger %>
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="text-[13px] font-bold text-[#0a1d13]">Þín spá: 2 - 1</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-slate-600 bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">+3 stig</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Rangt tákn (heimasigur), en Hræætan skilar 3 stigum vegna þess að heildarskekkjan er aðeins 1 mark (4 - 1 = 3).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
